{"tid":2492026,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[梁凌杰逝世22個月]  留下來的人 - C Allstar  <離開了的，我們存放心中>","createTime":"2021-04-16T18:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T17:19:03.000Z","uid":13644,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0bf623ecb1a72b35a7eef9c0666a92891f0fbd","tid":2492026,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:25:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-a02RxrYF24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-a02RxrYF24&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL%2BIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=5dd2c950\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-a02RxrYF24</a><br />\n<em>離開了的，我們存放心中<br />\n留下來的，我們好好生活<br />\n總會有一天<br />\n在世界的另一邊<br />\n彼此集合，好好相見 </em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWY8YV29vpp7e2CzxFHbKAi8GQx5ERXApVpaaDhSBw8GY?filename=P9jqDxJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9jqDxJ.png&h=167a81f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歌曲發佈時間 (<em>2021年4月15日= 梁手足逝世22個月</em>) 、簡介、以及MV一開始已經表明這首歌的意思。<br />\n留下來 的意思不論是留在這個城市或是留在這個世界，一樣感慨。<br />\n很多人說離開需要勇氣，有人會選擇離開自己成長的家，甚至有人已經被離開了這個世界；留下來所需要的勇氣可能更大。<br />\n<br />\n<em>可知留低的與重生的 卻在這邊<br />\n只可接受 新生活的蛻變</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQVNw72Fem7sEpEMDoyzHKVLQheb4boH7Fb23rsozKmfq?filename=WxWo9HE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxWo9HE.png&h=910c676b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nMV最後提到：<br />\n<em>人會死亡，信念仍在<br />\n那日終能在另一邊相見</em><br />\n<br />\n送上歌詞俾大家感受一下，希望大家繼續支持仍然敢發聲的歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>留下來的人</strong><br />\n曲：徐沛昕<br />\n詞：曰云<br />\n編：何秉舜<br />\n監：簡<br />\n<br />\n觀賞街景那動態 誰在半路停步<br />\n試聽著每顆心跳和脈膊起伏<br />\n拼了命成就幸福<br />\n世界在平衡著多少心痛 開始跟結束<br />\n<br />\n可呼吸多數萬次 難道這樣容易<br />\n你最後那一口氣呼了便化煙<br />\n為何明明在眼前 明明同行但你臨時別去 放下句點<br />\n<br />\n許多人都相信離開的人生走到該走的那時 痛著來話別<br />\n可知留低的與重生的 卻在這邊<br />\n怎撐過餘生的浩劫<br />\n<br />\n差不多三百日了 沉澱過又懷念<br />\n要記住你的一切 使世界亮了點<br />\n原來仍能活過來 仍能糊塗地愛悠然地笑 過著每天<br />\n<br />\n許多人都相信離開的<br />\n人生走到該走的那時 痛著來話別<br />\n可知留低的與重生的 卻在這邊<br />\n只可接受 新生活的蛻變<br />\n<br />\n祈求站在世界的終端相擁嗎<br />\n還能如常還能再對話<br />\n若到那天 地球還未塌下<br />\n尚能期待某種永遠嗎<br />\n<br />\n幾多人不捨那離開的 <br />\n誰都懂說生死都有時 <br />\n降淚時 又如何避免<br />\n留低的與重生的 也在這邊<br />\n即使費時一點 即使快樂不輕易 最後仍可遇見<br />\n<br />\n差不多九百日了 還是這樣懷念<br />\n説過在那一邊見 來待我出現<br />\n你繼續沿途歷險 <br />\n我繼續尋求幸福了 <br />\n那日見"},{"pid":"4db1557a6e15500ae67002069690def1f6ac79d7","tid":2492026,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:26:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3a3cdc769b900336cdf1881be5f72e85abb11b","tid":2492026,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b7a339eb3b3a4437b1dc8ed49fb66d8cd2b8f8","tid":2492026,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930795e8a98361c9f079e246981841e0621de09a","tid":2492026,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:27:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5456fdc8620f16c2efbe57aa0ae0123699474d82","tid":2492026,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85f07975f5a8b5907e2d49d77f3194fdf37803d","tid":2492026,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f939a619904b41bb9820299b7a19fcee8b7544","tid":2492026,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T18:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg